EN: He pleads with the judge for leniency in his case.

ZH: 她乞求父母允许她去参加这次旅行。
EN: She pleads with her parents to allow her to go on this trip.

ZH: 我乞求你，不要离开我一人。
EN: I beg of you, don't leave me alone.

ZH: 他们乞求教育部增加教育经费。
EN: They beseech the Ministry of Education to increase funding for education.

